<F P=102> BK1705150794 Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
in Cambodian 1300 GMT 17 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1705150794 </F>
<F P=104>  Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
