roundtable at my Chhanghsu-on residence near Pyongyang. I ask 
Your Excellency to give me a very clear and specific answer to 
the following question: Will Your Excellency attend the 
roundtable for national reconciliation and peace in Cambodia, 
that is, the roundtable which will be held at Chhanghsu-on on 27 
May? 
  With my deepest thanks, Excellency, please accept my highest 
regards. 
  [Signed] Norodom Sihanouk 

