<H4>    Khieu Samphan Agrees to Peace Talks </H4>

<F P=102> BK1905003794 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia in Cambodian 2330 GMT 18 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1905003794 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
