<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Seoul, May 17 (YONHAP) -- President Kim Yong-sam on 
Tuesday called upon the nation's scientists and science-related 
officials to redouble efforts to further develop science and 
technology. 
  While presiding over a meeting of the State Advisory Council 
for science and technology at Chongwadae [presidential office], 
President Kim emphasized the need of using available science 
resources most effectively because he said such resources are 
