  "The extent of our internationalization ranks 11th among 
developing countries, undermining our efforts to enhance the 
country's international competitiveness," Kim said. Following 
the meeting, President Kim hosted a luncheon at Chongwadae for 
the advisory council members led by chairman Yi Sang-ui. 

</TEXT>

