  [Text] Mr. He Zhiqiang, governor of Yunnan Province, 
People's Republic of China, and delegation called on Lieutenant 
General Thein Win, minister of transport, at the latter's office 
on Merchant Street at 0900 this morning. At the meeting cordial 
and frank talks were held on improving bilateral economic 
